casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Harold Lamont WALKER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 155198
COA: 327063 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 22, 2019

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to file a post-argument supplement to his brief is GRANTED. The supplement filed on February 20, 2019, is accepted for filing.
